  "texts": [
    "The study shows that users desire explanations for content recommendations to enable them to be better informed about the system and to be able to protect online privacy and security.",
    "The investigation reveals users' preferred explanation format and how explainability will affect users' behavior.",
    "We have observed that users need explanation due to the opacity of content recommendations, data privacy concerns, and the desire to rectify AI decision-making.",
    "Additionally, users require the explanation to be presented concisely and categorically, using layperson's terms, and visually in a controlled manner.",
    "XAI impacts the user's perception of bias, trust, and transparency and enhances informed decision-making."
  ],
